{"tid":1214631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[建制狗] 黃國健:昨示威是暴亂 警用適當武力","createTime":"2019-06-13T04:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T16:31:48.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4a1d9ebe6dbeba79225799348e1e8d76499a4c12","tid":1214631,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:53:14.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員、工聯會立法會議員黃國健表示，他支持修訂《逃犯條例》的立場不變，因此要返回立法會盡責審議草案。<br />\n<br />\n黃國健認為，昨日的示威活動是暴亂，如果香港是一個國家，例如中歐、東歐小國，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">昨日的情況足以令政府倒台</span></strong>，反對派就可上台，但香港是中國一個特區，反對派才搞不成事。<br />\n<br />\n黃國健對昨日情況感到心痛和心寒，年輕人無必要採取激進手法，損害了香港國際形象。他又認為，警方昨日的清場行動適合，示威者幾乎衝入立法會，警方才使用適當武力，已非常忍讓，相比世界各地，香港的警察是最斯文。<br />\n<br />\n他又指出，建制派昨日原本準備回到立法會開會，但情況不容許，要另找地方。"},{"pid":"fb7fa3231c2500a38e5495106b8ac8960190df79","tid":1214631,"uid":47776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:54:22.000Z","msg":"哦<br />\nnoted"},{"pid":"aa6a5e1899406611d34e69ffc7dbdeee6132b516","tid":1214631,"uid":197157,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:56:03.000Z","msg":"昨日的情況足以令政府倒台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba73db9e285271bcc60aac3d96458d5b5e43b6b","tid":1214631,"uid":170967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:01:39.000Z","msg":"示威影響國際形象？不如你睇下國際社會點睇鎮壓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />擺到明係警犬同政府影響香港國際影像"},{"pid":"68231af0677f38103649ef78860351ce242c8438","tid":1214631,"uid":45120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:04:25.000Z","msg":"相比世界各地，香港的示威者是最斯文。<br />\n<br />\n我諗世界各地都搵唔到有差佬會冇警告就開槍<br />\n都唔會搵到堆鐵馬同拎下摭就開槍加催淚彈"},{"pid":"547c6c795be9987dff975e03ae81b146597a96b3","tid":1214631,"uid":186454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:20:33.000Z","msg":"咁67年嗰次係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n恐襲？"},{"pid":"47f86b2429a69e404c23d1bbfe4dc3cab50ff0d0","tid":1214631,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"547c6c795be9987dff975e03ae81b146597a96b3","tid":1214631,"uid":186454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:20:33.000Z","msg":"咁67年嗰次係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n恐襲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:21:35.000Z","msg":"官民互動"},{"pid":"15ff7463f9e9404c95fefbe951e3721e165320d1","tid":1214631,"uid":22326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa6a5e1899406611d34e69ffc7dbdeee6132b516","tid":1214631,"uid":197157,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:56:03.000Z","msg":"昨日的情況足以令政府倒台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:21:47.000Z","msg":"咁個政府都幾廢下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0a3f5dc8716982762ce83666b9ef2b89b6ea2e","tid":1214631,"uid":14478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:22:41.000Z","msg":"工聯會最有資格評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e379eabb9ab29047441044cf6eae54da855292","tid":1214631,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:31:48.000Z","msg":"係咪曲線港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}